---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/Footer.astro";
import { techniques } from "../data/techniques";
---

<Layout title="About — VibeBalm">
  <Header />

  <article class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 py-16 sm:py-24">
    <!-- Intro -->
    <p class="text-sage-600 text-lg mb-12 leading-relaxed">
      VibeBalm is a free collection of evidence-based mental health techniques — designed to help you manage anxiety, overcome procrastination, and build lasting psychological resilience.
    </p>

    <!-- Creator -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-sage-900 mb-6">Hi, we're VibeBalm 👋</h2>
      <div class="text-sage-700 text-lg leading-relaxed space-y-4">
        <p>
          Anxiety, procrastination, burnout, perfectionism, self-criticism — these aren't character flaws. They're patterns. And like all patterns, they can be understood, interrupted, and rewired.
        </p>
        <p>
          We built VibeBalm because we noticed something: the internet is full of mental health advice, but very little of it is <em>actionable</em>. Most articles tell you to "be mindful" or "just start." But they don't tell you <strong>how</strong> — step by step, in the moment, when your brain is fighting against you.
        </p>
        <p>
          So we went to the source. Every technique on VibeBalm is grounded in established psychological frameworks — CBT, DBT, ACT, MBSR — and distilled into clear, 2-minute guides that you can use right now. No jargon. No sign-up. No paywall on the content.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Stats -->
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-8 justify-center mb-16">
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-sage-900">{techniques.length}</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-sage-500 mt-1">Techniques</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-sage-900">5</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-sage-500 mt-1">Categories</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-sage-900">8</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-sage-500 mt-1">Frameworks</div>
      </div>
      <div class="text-center">
        <div class="text-4xl font-bold text-sage-900">100%</div>
        <div class="text-sm text-sage-500 mt-1">Free</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Mission -->
    <div class="mb-16 bg-sage-50 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-sage-200">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-sage-900 mb-4">Our Mission</h2>
      <div class="text-sage-700 leading-relaxed space-y-3">
        <p>
          <strong>Make mental health tools accessible, actionable, and stigma-free.</strong>
        </p>
        <p>
          We believe everyone deserves access to techniques that actually work — not just vague wellness platitudes. You shouldn't need a therapist's referral to learn how to interrupt a panic attack or break a procrastination loop. These are human skills, and VibeBalm exists to democratize them.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- What you'll find -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-sage-900 mb-6">What You'll Find Here</h2>
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 sm:grid-cols-2 gap-6">
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-sage-200">
          <span class="text-2xl block mb-3">🧠</span>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-sage-900 mb-2">18 Proven Techniques</h3>
          <p class="text-sage-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Each one sourced from clinical psychology, with clear step-by-step instructions and real-world applications.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-sage-200">
          <span class="text-2xl block mb-3">📁</span>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-sage-900 mb-2">5 Problem Categories</h3>
          <p class="text-sage-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Organized by the challenge you're facing — from chronic procrastination to acute anxiety — so you find the right tool fast.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-sage-200">
          <span class="text-2xl block mb-3">📱</span>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-sage-900 mb-2">Phone Wallpapers</h3>
          <p class="text-sage-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Beautiful reminders you carry on your lock screen. Every time you unlock your phone, a technique is there.</p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-white rounded-xl p-6 border border-sage-200">
          <span class="text-2xl block mb-3">🆓</span>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-sage-900 mb-2">100% Free Content</h3>
          <p class="text-sage-600 text-sm leading-relaxed">Every technique guide is free forever. No sign-up required. No content paywall. Mental health should never be gated.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Important disclaimer -->
    <div class="mb-16 bg-amber-50 rounded-2xl p-6 border border-amber-200">
      <div class="flex items-start gap-3">
        <span class="text-amber-600 text-xl mt-0.5">⚠️</span>
        <div>
          <h3 class="font-bold text-amber-900 mb-2">Important</h3>
          <p class="text-amber-800 text-sm leading-relaxed">
            VibeBalm is an educational resource, not a substitute for professional mental health care. If you are experiencing severe anxiety, depression, suicidal thoughts, or any mental health crisis, please reach out to a qualified professional or a crisis helpline. You are not alone, and help is available.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Suggestion form -->
    <div class="mb-16">
      <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-sage-900 mb-4">Suggestions & Feedback</h2>
      <p class="text-sage-600 mb-6 leading-relaxed">
        Have a technique you'd like us to add? Found an error? Want to share your experience? We'd love to hear from you.
      </p>
      <form id="suggestion-form" class="space-y-4">
        <div>
          <label for="s-name" class="block text-sm font-medium text-sage-700 mb-1">Your name <span class="text-sage-400">(optional)</span></label>
          <input
            type="text"
            id="s-name"
            maxlength="100"
            placeholder="Anonymous is fine"
            class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-sage-200 bg-white text-sage-900 placeholder:text-sage-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sage-400 focus:border-transparent transition"
          />
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="s-type" class="block text-sm font-medium text-sage-700 mb-1">Type</label>
          <select
            id="s-type"
            class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-sage-200 bg-white text-sage-900 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sage-400 focus:border-transparent transition"
          >
            <option value="">Select a category...</option>
            <option value="new-technique">Suggest a new technique</option>
            <option value="correction">Report an error</option>
            <option value="experience">Share my experience</option>
            <option value="feature">Feature request</option>
            <option value="other">Other</option>
          </select>
        </div>
        <div>
          <label for="s-msg" class="block text-sm font-medium text-sage-700 mb-1">Your message</label>
          <textarea
            id="s-msg"
            rows="5"
            maxlength="5000"
            placeholder="Tell us what's on your mind..."
            class="w-full px-4 py-3 rounded-xl border border-sage-200 bg-white text-sage-900 placeholder:text-sage-400 focus:outline-none focus:ring-2 focus:ring-sage-400 focus:border-transparent transition resize-none"
          ></textarea>
        </div>
        <div id="s-error" class="hidden text-rose-600 text-sm"></div>
        <button
          type="submit"
          class="bg-sage-800 hover:bg-sage-700 text-white font-semibold px-8 py-3 rounded-full transition-all duration-200 hover:shadow-lg hover:-translate-y-0.5"
        >
          Send Suggestion
        </button>
      </form>
      <div id="s-success" class="hidden mt-6 p-4 bg-green-50 border border-green-200 rounded-xl">
        <p class="text-green-800 font-medium">✅ Thank you for your suggestion! We read every submission and will review it soon.</p>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- Contact -->
    <div class="text-sage-500 text-sm leading-relaxed">
      <p>
        You can also reach us at <a href="mailto:hello@vibebalm.co" class="text-sage-700 hover:text-sage-900 underline underline-offset-2 transition-colors">hello@vibebalm.co</a> if you'd prefer email.
      </p>
    </div>
  </article>

  <Footer />
</Layout>

<script define:vars={{ storageKey: 'vibebalm_suggestions' }}>
  // Load stored suggestions for display
  const stored = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(storageKey) || '[]');

  const form = document.getElementById('suggestion-form');
  const successMsg = document.getElementById('s-success');
  const errorMsg = document.getElementById('s-error');

  form?.addEventListener('submit', (e) => {
    e.preventDefault();
    errorMsg?.classList.add('hidden');

    const name = document.getElementById('s-name')?.value?.trim() || 'Anonymous';
    const type = document.getElementById('s-type')?.value || 'other';
    const message = document.getElementById('s-msg')?.value?.trim();

    if (!message) {
      errorMsg.textContent = 'Please enter a message.';
      errorMsg.classList.remove('hidden');
      return;
    }

    // Save to localStorage
    const suggestions = JSON.parse(localStorage.getItem(storageKey) || '[]');
    suggestions.push({
      id: Date.now().toString(36) + Math.random().toString(36).slice(2, 6),
      name,
      type,
      message,
      timestamp: new Date().toISOString(),
    });
    localStorage.setItem(storageKey, JSON.stringify(suggestions));

    // Show success
    form.style.display = 'none';
    successMsg?.classList.remove('hidden');
  });
</script>
